select top 1 [DESCRIPTION], GCM_NUM , GCM_NOTE1 from sys_gcm (nolock) where condition = 'TXANNOUNCE' and gcm_id = 'MESSAGE' and FACTIVE = 'Y' and DATEDIFF(SECOND, DATEADD(SECOND, GCM_NUM, '1970-01-01'), GETDATE()) <= :1 and GCM_NUM > :2
